section.section:
In Somerset County, the committee consists of the following eight members:
one member appointed by the Governor and nominated by the Senator from Legislative District 38;
three members appointed by the Governor, each one nominated by a different Delegate from Legislative District 38;
three members appointed by the Governor to provide, to the extent possible, legal, law enforcement, and business representatives on the committee; and
a Somerset County Commissioner appointed by the Board of County Commissioners of Somerset County.
